-title\">French Pedicure</h3>\n        <p class=\"tile-subtitle\">Soft pink, perfect white</p>\n        <p class=\"tile-desc\">Shapes and cares for your feet, finishing with a soft pink base and clean white tips for a classic, polished look.</p>\n        <div class=\"tile-footer\">\n          <div class=\"tile-price\">\n<sup>AED </sup>116</div>\n          <div class=\"tile-dur\">1 hr</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"tile\" data-reveal data-delay=\"160\">\n        <p class=\"tile-tag\">French · Polish</p>\n        <h3 class=\"tile-title\">French Polish</h3>\n        <p class=\"tile-subtitle\">The classic look that never fades</p>\n        <p class=\"tile-desc\">Soft pink or nude base paired with clean white tips for a neat, natural finish.</p>\n        <div class=\"tile-footer\">\n          <div class=\"tile-price\">\n<sup>AED </sup>53</div>\n          <div class=\"tile-dur\">40 min</div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<!-- ════════════════ POLISH & EXTRAS ════════════════ -->\n<section class=\"section\">\n  <div class=\"section-inner\">\n    <div class=\"section-label\" data-reveal>\n      <span class=\"section-label-text\">Polish & Essentials</span>\n      <div class=\"section-label-line\"></div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"price-table\" data-reveal>\n      <div class=\"pt-header\">\n        <span>Service</span>\n        <span>Duration</span>\n        <span>Price</span>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pt-row gel\">\n        <div class=\"pt-name\">Gel Polish<small class=\"blush\">Gel · Shine that lasts — cured under LED/UV for a smooth, shiny finish</small>\n</div>\n        <div class=\"pt-dur\">1 hr</div>\n        <div class=\"pt-price\">\n<sup>AED </sup>74</div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"pt-row\">\n        <div class=\"pt-name\">Classic Polish<small>Classic shine, everyday style</small>\n</div>\n        <div class=\"pt-dur\">30 min</div>\n        <div class=\"pt-price\">\n<sup>AED </sup>48<